From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: akolliasAMD <akollias@amd.com>
Date: Fri, 5 Jun 2026 00:00:01 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 2/2] Replace TBB symbol-version scripts with
 AMDROCM_SYSDEPS_1.0 map

Upstream oneTBB links each .so with -Wl,--version-script=<lib>.def to
export only the documented symbols under TBB_*. Overwrite those scripts
with a broad AMDROCM_SYSDEPS_1.0 catch-all so the sysdeps versioning
scheme applies uniformly across all bundled libraries.
---
 src/tbb/def/lin32-tbb.def               | 170 +-----------------------
 src/tbb/def/lin64-tbb.def               | 170 +-----------------------
 src/tbbmalloc/def/lin32-tbbmalloc.def   |  74 +----------
 src/tbbmalloc/def/lin64-tbbmalloc.def   |  74 +----------
 src/tbbmalloc_proxy/def/lin32-proxy.def |  56 +-------
 src/tbbmalloc_proxy/def/lin64-proxy.def |  56 +-------
 6 files changed, 12 insertions(+), 588 deletions(-)

